Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.11,0:00:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 炮擊沒個消停
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.24,0:00:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃個飯都不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.28,0:00:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒工夫抱怨這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.62,0:00:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和前線比起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.79,0:00:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼看都是我們地勢不利
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.00,0:00:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不光如此 對方的射程明顯遠得多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.84,0:00:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是用了新型清澄?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.43,0:01:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是吧 恐怕騎士團的神通都搭載上了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.31,0:01:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是新型清澄的威力···
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.99,0:01:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能用的新型清澄都裝上了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.70,0:01:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說明對方也很拼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.62,0:01:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟這裡是生命線
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.29,0:01:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我們也來說也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.16,0:01:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能突破這裡 就能一口氣進攻首都了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.04,0:01:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是時候各就各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.96,0:01:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快輪到我們上了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.51,0:01:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.64,0:01:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤回前言 暫時待命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.93,0:01:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕作戰有變
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.10,0:01:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.56,0:01:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僵局遲遲不破 怕是沒耐心了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.57,0:01:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,福利特參謀長站出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.16,0:03:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了打破目前的僵局
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.54,0:03:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將派出別動隊執行作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能確定的是 敵軍在舌狀高地城中布了陣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.84,0:03:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們無法從下方觀察到他們的準確位置
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.68,0:03:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.51,0:03:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在敵軍據點後方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.52,0:03:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是南方森林裡 已經派出部隊潛入
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.06,0:03:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是當時的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個位置的橋沒斷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.19,0:04:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備從這裡派別動隊包抄敵軍後方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.49,0:04:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於編制
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.87,0:04:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 赫希分隊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.74,0:04:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.70,0:04:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙夫分隊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.04,0:04:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.87,0:04:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有比爾格分隊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.50,0:04:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.46,0:04:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休伊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是休伊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.25,0:04:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史黛拉 還有莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.76,0:04:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.38,0:04:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們認識?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.18,0:04:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是新兵時待過同一座基地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.14,0:04:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能這麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.35,0:04:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時都這麼照顧你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.39,0:04:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那是欺負人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.85,0:04:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來現在有點進步了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.61,0:04:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時看你這麼不成熟還擔心過你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.40,0:04:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是沒變化嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.86,0:04:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就很沉著 一直都在笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.45,0:04:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這裡是為了下次作戰?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.87,0:04:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 現在在赫希分隊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.50,0:04:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說要打總體戰 規模比之前更大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見 要活著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心 我賊運好得很
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.51,0:05:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是這麼不可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.06,0:05:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你們沒少被訓過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.06,0:05:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這些前輩人都很好 就是嘴上不善
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.98,0:05:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不面善
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.65,0:05:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都進去 說明作戰計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.11,0:05:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁夜色沿這條路線迂迴往南
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.28,0:05:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿過右手邊支流往西 前面就是橋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.91,0:05:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們打頭陣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.29,0:05:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一在抵達前被發現了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.80,0:05:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點已經想好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.67,0:05:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被發現 順勢作為佯攻要員也能起作用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.05,0:05:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,委婉地讓我們當誘餌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.72,0:05:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想這樣就別讓人發現
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.02,0:05:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:05:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過橋穿出森林
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.27,0:06:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能確認敵軍的位置 就發信號彈通知總隊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.82,0:06:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炮擊開始後 我們也從後方疆擾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.82,0:06:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全軍攻入敵軍陣地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.53,0:06:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能這麼順利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.24,0:06:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人在森林裡也安排了守衛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.91,0:06:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主力集中到了前線 後方勢必較薄弱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.21,0:06:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都考慮到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.88,0:06:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點整開始作戰 深夜的森林裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.51,0:06:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.22,0:06:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.60,0:06:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要沒人突然提出分頭行動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.89,0:06:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這你就多慮了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.44,0:06:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次作戰不簡單 不能全權交給你們執行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.32,0:06:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都記好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.57,0:06:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是看不透他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.49,0:06:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也沒弄明白他為什麼來分隊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.37,0:06:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是為了錢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.95,0:06:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.50,0:07:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前我在駐屯地看到他匯款
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.79,0:07:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時正好在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.25,0:07:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有家人 匯款很正常
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.26,0:07:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是給姘頭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.38,0:07:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是數額不小
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.01,0:07:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會計也忍不住問了要匯給誰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.89,0:07:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長怎麼回答的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.56,0:07:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.89,0:07:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說有一個大隊的小鳥嗷嗷待哺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.78,0:07:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.98,0:07:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙艷福不淺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.15,0:07:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說他很厲害略
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.41,0:07:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.99,0:07:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.83,0:07:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.66,0:07:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 知道是什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.60,0:07:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右手邊 看見支流了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.01,0:08:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續前進兩公里 過河後往西出發
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.61,0:08:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翻過山丘應該就看得見那座橋了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.79,0:08:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.25,0:08:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通知後面的隊伍也停下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.92,0:08:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.30,0:08:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神通？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.96,0:08:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是遺棄的殘骸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.97,0:08:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是用來當碉堡的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.67,0:08:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正躲在裡面監視著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.34,0:08:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要動手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.72,0:08:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要動手就一口氣解決 不讓他們聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.47,0:08:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周圍有神通嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.48,0:08:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.07,0:09:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右側12度 距離203
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.62,0:09:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仰角17
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.96,0:09:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 18度
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.79,0:09:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0K 要打了 退後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.69,0:09:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 回去略
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.65,0:09:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.95,0:09:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:09:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.51,0:10:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是腳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.01,0:10:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來沒斷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.68,0:10:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還算走運
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.31,0:10:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我的神通擋住了 才沒更嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.19,0:10:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼走運的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.98,0:10:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是你中了陷阱 也不會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.78,0:10:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛···
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.57,0:10:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來這人的確賊運好得很
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.70,0:10:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個踉蹌 避開了直擊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.83,0:10:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這下不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.66,0:10:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 我平時鍛鍊過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.58,0:10:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後續隊伍有衛生兵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.63,0:10:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都沒帶 畢竟只想著前進
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.55,0:10:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該有一輛支援車輛跟著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.14,0:10:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓它來接···
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.14,0:10:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我還能繼續戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.47,0:10:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.64,0:10:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.56,0:10:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 史黛拉姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.56,0:10:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車馬上來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.45,0:11:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史黛拉姐···
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.03,0:11:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想有人拖後腿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.07,0:11:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過分了 我還能戰鬥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.66,0:11:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不算了 人家自己都說能戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.13,0:11:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了再補充人員就行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.59,0:11:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 太差勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.55,0:11:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛···
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.80,0:11:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懂了 你們先走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.69,0:11:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個···
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.52,0:11:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.07,0:11:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你費心了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.28,0:11:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會治療啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.16,0:11:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟一直在照顧新傷不斷的人 都膩了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.00,0:11:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 畢竟在戰場上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.59,0:11:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.84,0:12:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 隊長為什麼來我們分隊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.80,0:12:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾年了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.64,0:12:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你加入這個分隊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.01,0:12:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩年了 一開始只有史黛拉姐和莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.06,0:12:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久休伊也從別的部隊調過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.77,0:12:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還是和新兵一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.78,0:12:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直被小看 戲弄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.41,0:12:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他隊員都戰死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.74,0:12:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.70,0:12:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換過幾個人後 來了布雷克兵曹長和皮爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.38,0:12:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我覺得能走到今天很不容易了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.34,0:12:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了史黛拉姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.05,0:12:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很信任她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.14,0:12:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 被她救過好幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.31,0:12:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邊境部隊曽發起過政變吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.44,0:13:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次鎮壓 出乎意料地艱難
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.78,0:13:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方準備抵抗到底
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.74,0:13:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最後雙方子彈耗盡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.70,0:13:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成了肉搏戰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.46,0:13:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然莉莉都快沒力氣反擊了· · ·
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.51,0:13:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.85,0:13:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史黛拉姐也耗盡了子彈 束手無策
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.69,0:13:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話我很驚訝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.41,0:13:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直很冷靜的史黛拉姐會這麼亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.08,0:13:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會來救莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.71,0:13:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她以前就是那樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.17,0:13:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.33,0:14:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不透她的真心 總是假裝出一副笑臉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.17,0:14:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你見過她發自內心的笑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.43,0:14:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.94,0:14:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.02,0:14:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們到橋邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.23,0:14:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後續部隊到達之前暫時待命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.36,0:14:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白我們也過來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.90,0:14:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後你自行判斷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.82,0:14:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果覺得自己不會拖後腿就跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.70,0:14:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個···
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.79,0:14:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 就覺得自己好像多嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.38,0:14:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長很善於傾聽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.13,0:14:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,習慣和小孩打交道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.88,0:14:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.23,0:15:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著組成一隊 穿過森林
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.73,0:15:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口氣從目標背後進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.53,0:15:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預計有不少兵力在森林中把守
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.49,0:15:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使交戰 也要儘量讓一個分隊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.70,0:15:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少讓一架神通抵達目的地 完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.40,0:15:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傅立葉兵曹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.29,0:16:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我們分隊吸引火力 你們先走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.25,0:16:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.08,0:16:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去騎士型那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.25,0:16:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃傑 厄普頓跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.09,0:16:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓋伊 歐根對付剩下的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.09,0:16:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.80,0:16:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面也有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.18,0:16:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙在這邊 走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.26,0:16:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.26,0:16:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走 克萊頓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.72,0:16:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.52,0:16:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摧毀一架
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.06,0:16:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一樣 但是· ··
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.06,0:16:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.15,0:16:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯繫不上同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.82,0:16:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.03,0:16:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.32,0:16:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.04,0:16:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別拖拖拉拉的 皮爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.09,0:16:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 第二架了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.34,0:16:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比爾格···分隊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.59,0:16:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比爾格分隊 聽得見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.97,0:16:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是蓋伊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.77,0:17:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歐根被幹掉了 大家也都無法行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.44,0:17:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙一架機體···
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.52,0:17:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被幹掉了？歐根死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.81,0:17:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去 休伊 布雷克 皮爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.44,0:17:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管我們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.74,0:17:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.33,0:17:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休伊 你先走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.62,0:17:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.84,0:17:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓋伊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.34,0:17:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休伊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.59,0:17:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.09,0:17:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.55,0:17:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙很快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.77,0:17:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.51,0:18:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史黛拉姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.03,0:18:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.95,0:18:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼亂打一通是打不中的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.72,0:19:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壞了?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.40,0:19:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.58,0:19:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別動 莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.80,0:19:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.84,0:19:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別追了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.51,0:19:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.35,0:19:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是沒能順利擊敗他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.06,0:19:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像那時候的史黛拉姐一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.48,0:19:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.10,0:19:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.23,0:19:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來這下真的動不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.23,0:20:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是狼狽不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.57,0:20:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少呼嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.95,0:20:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.07,0:20:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收拾掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.07,0:20:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是赫希分隊全機嚴重受損
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.87,0:20:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有人戰死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.08,0:20:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.37,0:20:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還得意地叫別人活下來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.46,0:20:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能笑笑了 淨是這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.68,0:20:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信號彈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.77,0:20:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來沙夫分隊找到了敵軍據點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.35,0:20:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要開始總攻了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.73,0:20:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉 這次一定要等支援車輛來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.86,0:20:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.61,0:20:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的增壓器也用盡了嗎 還能打嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.87,0:20:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然可以 走著爬著也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.46,0:20:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 死了再補充人員就行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.17,0:21:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越是被這麼說 越可能活下來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.84,0:21:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 從目標背後疆擾敵軍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.80,0:21:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.64,0:21:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.40,0:21:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.27,0:21:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.36,0:21:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.54,0:21:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.88,0:21:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.97,0:21:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史黛拉姐發自內心的笑容
